==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wringer
<hw>Wring"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who,
or that which, wrings; hence, an extortioner.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A machine for pressing water out of anything,
particularly from clothes after they have been washed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wringing</ent>⟦br⟧
